msgctxt "68_Akiyama"
msgid "Hmm? What're you doing here?"
msgstr "¿Mmm? ¿Qué haces acá?"

msgctxt "80_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Oh... Akiyama-san."
msgstr "Ah... Akiyama-san."

msgctxt "92_Akiyama"
msgid "Hey. Don't worry about taking some time off. If you feel like it's going to help, take as much time as you need."
msgstr "Oye, no me importa si te tomas un descanso. Si sientes que te va a hacer sentir mejor, tómate el tiempo que quieras."

msgctxt "104_Akiyama"
msgid "So how are things going? Found any decent guys yet?"
msgstr "So how are things going? Found any decent guys yet?"

msgctxt "116_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Haha! I mean, I have a lot of rich customers, but as men they... leave something to be desired, if you catch my drift."
msgstr "Haha! I mean, I have a lot of rich customers, but as men they... leave something to be desired, if you catch my drift."

msgctxt "128_Akiyama"
msgid "It's a hard road finding the perfect man, I've heard."
msgstr "It's a hard road finding the perfect man, I've heard."

msgctxt "140_Akiyama"
msgid "How's your day job going? I imagine they keep you pretty busy."
msgstr "How's your day job going? I imagine they keep you pretty busy."

msgctxt "152_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Actually, they've put me completely in charge of a project. So I'm busy, but I love it!"
msgstr "Actually, they've put me completely in charge of a project. So I'm busy, but I love it!"

msgctxt "164_Akiyama"
msgid "Sounds like you're a natural leader. You could probably quit the company and work for yourself."
msgstr "Sounds like you're a natural leader. You could probably quit the company and work for yourself."

msgctxt "176_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Work for myself? I'd never thought of that..."
msgstr "Work for myself? I'd never thought of that..."

msgctxt "188_キャバ育名前"
msgid "Hmm..."
msgstr "Mmm..."

msgctxt "200_Akiyama"
msgid "(I think she'll do just fine.)"
msgstr "(I think she'll do just fine.)"

